::Savanna:;

"He's what?! OK, I'm out of here."
She looked at Blurr, "I got to go and help them.  Sorry to leave you 
all alone, but I have to help.  Cya when I get back."

She ran out of the autobot ship and ran to Kluster's position. She 
homed in on his signal and ran as fast as her lion legs could carry 
her.
